The patch file in this directory are designed to be applied on top of amg2013 v2.3.

Source code:
    https://asc.llnl.gov/CORAL-benchmarks/Throughput/amg20130624.tgz

Installation:

1. Acquire the source:
    wget https://asc.llnl.gov/CORAL-benchmarks/Throughput/amg20130624.tgz

2. Unpack the source:
    tar zxvf amg20130624.tgz

3. Change directories to the unpacked files.
    cd AMG2013

4. Patch nekbone with the patch utility:
    patch -p1 < ../0001-Adding-geopm-markup-to-AMG.patch

5. Profit.

---------------------------------------------------------------------

Source code for CORAL 2 AMG v1.7:
    https://asc.llnl.gov/coral-2-benchmarks/downloads/AMG-master-5.zip

Installation:

1. Acquire the source:
    wget https://asc.llnl.gov/coral-2-benchmarks/downloads/AMG-master-5.zip

2. Unpack the source:
    unzip AMG-master-5.zip

3. Change directories to the unpacked files:
    cd AMG-master

4. Patch MiniFE with the patch utility:
    patch -p1 < ../0001-Adding-geopm-markup-to-CORAL-2-AMG.patch

5. Profit.
